Cell C has unveiled a new Black Friday 2018 deal, offering 50GB of mobile data for R500. The network said that starting on Black Friday – 23 November – customers can buy a prepaid data SIM loaded with 50GB for R500. The deal is subject to stock availability, and will run until 25 November at Cell C stores. “Simply pop the SIM in a router to connect your holiday spot or slide it into a tablet and keep your kids entertained all the way to your holiday destination,” said Junaid Munshi, Cell C Chief Commercial Officer. The data will be valid for six months from activation and can be used at anytime of the day.